that&#39;s what I was doing when I heard it. Often they talk about what I&#39;m 
doing at any given moment, regardless of when it was recorded. Some may 
notice, my &quot;guys&quot; almost always refer to me a in the feminine, one reason 
why I hate to post too many of those. With regular spirit contact, it&#39;s the 
opposite.

The only difference with this box is the echo box. Because I had to fit a 
box a small area, I made it a wave guide echo box, and maybe most important, 
I made it out of soft steel from a computer case. The wave guide box has 
channels that make the box acoustically larger, like a Bose Wave Radio.

Thanks for listening.

Frank-S


